Similar configuration can also be applied globally for collections:

    ObjectMapper mapper = objectMapperBuilder()
        .changeDefaultNullHandling(n -&gt; n.withContentNulls(Nulls.AS_EMPTY))
        .build();

Or by type:

    ObjectMapper mapper = objectMapperBuilder()
        .withConfigOverride(List.class,
            o -&gt; o.setNullHandling(JsonSetter.Value.forContentNulls(Nulls.AS_EMPTY)))
        .build();

